OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly dry day. A sunny start
OL,6,Fin the west but otherwise quite cloudy
OL,7,Fwith the odd spot of light rain
OL,8,Fpossible in the east. Cloud clearing
OL,9,Fthrough the morning to leave good
OL,10,Fsunny spells across the region.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will stay dry throughout
OL,13,Fthe evening and overnight. Some
OL,14,Fprolonged spells of evening sunshine
OL,15,Fleading to clear spells overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FDry and warm with lengthy
OL,18,Fsunny spells for much of the day, but
OL,19,Fsunshine turning somewhat hazier as
OL,20,Fcloud spreads south in the afternoon
OL,21,Fand evening. Warmer in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
